28 JAN UPDATE

scipt now generates a unique html file and converts it to a .mobi file using kindlegen. Some minor encoding issues still. (works fine in the browser but kindlegen mangles it. Only lead I found online was to use HTML entities ("&" characters)). That should be accepted by kindlegen.

25 JAN UPDATE

script can now create a unique html file. Pointers on how that file should be formatted : https://www.aliciaramirez.com/2014/05/how-to-make-a-kindle-ebook-from-scratch/ (very good article)

